                            <comment id="12910393" author="jdcryans" created="Thu, 16 Sep 2010 23:34:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch that adds the desired behavior. It requires that the family is configured to only keep one version and that the Put is done only one cell. It&apos;s kinda hacky.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12916280" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 29 Sep 2010 20:13:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch fixes an important issue about memstore size when putting multiple columns that the previous patch introduces.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
